{
  "info": {
    "name": "MiniMax AI Platform",
    "description": "MiniMax 大模型平台 API 完整测试集（V5.9）。\n\n## 快速开始\n1. 先调用 `Auth > Login` 获取 Token\n2. 自动填充全局变量 `{{accessToken}}`\n3. 所有需鉴权的请求会自动携带 `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`\n\n## 环境变量\n| Variable | Value | 说明 |\n|----------|-------|------|\n| baseUrl | http://localhost:7080 | Gateway 地址 |\n| accessToken | | 登录后自动填充 |\n| refreshToken | | 登录后自动填充 |\n| userId | 1 | 当前用户 ID |\n| sessionId | | 会话 ID（创建后自动填充）|\n| kbId | | 知识库 ID |\n| toolId | | 工具 ID |\n\n## 限流提示\n- 默认公开端点无需 Token\n- 管理端点需 ADMIN 角色 Token\n- 聊天端点默认 60 req/min",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:7080"},
    {"key": "accessToken", "value": ""},
    {"key": "refreshToken", "value": ""},
    {"key": "userId", "value": "1"},
    {"key": "sessionId", "value": ""},
    {"key": "kbId", "value": ""},
    {"key": "toolId", "value": ""},
    {"key": "apiKey", "value": ""}
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "登录",
          "event": [
            {"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
              "    if (jsonData.data.userInfo) {",
              "      pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', jsonData.data.userInfo.id);",
              "    }",
              "  }",
              "}",
              "pm.test('登录成功 code=0', function() {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.eql(0);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('返回 accessToken', function() {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.expect(jsonData.data.accessToken).to.be.a('string');",
              "});"
            ]}}
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin@123\"\n}", "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}},
            "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]}
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "注册",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"testuser\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123456\",\n  \"nickname\": \"TestUser\",\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\"\n}", "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}},
            "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]}
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token 续期",
          "event": [
            {"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
              "  }",
              "}"
            ]}}
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}", "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}},
            "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]}
